trans-unit.source: Represents a WS-Federation Sign-Out Cleanup message.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en WS Federation Sign-Out opprydding-melding.

trans-unit.source: The message is created when the received message has the action parameter (wa) set to “wsignoutcleanup1.0”.
trans-unit.target: Meldingen opprettes når den mottatte meldingen er handlingsparameter (wa) som er satt til "wsignoutcleanup1.0".

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.SignOutCleanupRequestMessage"></xref> class with the specified base URL.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.SignOutCleanupRequestMessage"> </xref> klassen med den angitte primær URL-adressen.

trans-unit.source: The wa message parameter (the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationMessage.Action%2A> property) is initialized to “wsignoutcleanup1.0”.
trans-unit.target: Parameteren wa melding (den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationMessage.Action%2A>egenskapen) initialiseres til "wsignoutcleanup1.0".</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationMessage.Action%2A>

trans-unit.source: The base URL to which this message applies.
trans-unit.target: Den primære URL-adressen som gjelder for meldingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.SignOutCleanupRequestMessage"></xref> class with the specified base URL and wreply parameter.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.SignOutCleanupRequestMessage"> </xref> klassen med den angitte base URL-adresse og wreply-parameteren.

trans-unit.source: The wa message parameter (the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationMessage.Action%2A> property) is initialized to “wsignoutcleanup1.0”.
trans-unit.target: Parameteren wa melding (den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationMessage.Action%2A>egenskapen) initialiseres til "wsignoutcleanup1.0".</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationMessage.Action%2A>

trans-unit.source: The base URL to which this message applies.
trans-unit.target: Den primære URL-adressen som gjelder for meldingen.

trans-unit.source: The value of the wreply parameter.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for parameteren wreply.

trans-unit.source: The URL to which the reply should be sent.
trans-unit.target: URL-adressen som skal sendes svaret.

trans-unit.source: reply is either empty or .
trans-unit.target: replyer enten tom eller .

trans-unit.source: -or- reply is not a valid URI.
trans-unit.target: - eller - reply er ikke en gyldig URI.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the wreply parameter of the message.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir parameteren wreply for meldingen.

trans-unit.source: Set to `null` or an empty string to remove the wreply parameter from the message.
trans-unit.target: Satt til `null` eller en tom streng til å fjerne parameteren wreply fra meldingen.

trans-unit.source: The value of the wreply parameter.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for parameteren wreply.

trans-unit.source: This is the URL to which the reply should be sent.
trans-unit.target: Dette er svaret skal sendes til URL-adressen.

trans-unit.source: An attempt to set a value that is not a valid, absolute URI occurs.
trans-unit.target: Et forsøk på å angi en verdi som ikke er en gyldig, absolutt URI forekommer.

trans-unit.source: Validates the current instance.
trans-unit.target: Validerer gjeldende forekomst.

trans-unit.source: The wa parameter (the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationMessage.Action*> property) is not set to “wsignoutcleanup1.0”.
trans-unit.target: Parameteren wa (den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationMessage.Action*>egenskapen) er ikke satt til "wsignoutcleanup1.0".</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationMessage.Action*>

trans-unit.source: Writes the message in query string form to the specified text writer.
trans-unit.target: Skriver meldingen i skjemaet for spørringen streng til den angitte tekstskriver.

trans-unit.source: This method calls the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SignOutCleanupRequestMessage.Validate%2A> method before writing the message.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kaller den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SignOutCleanupRequestMessage.Validate%2A>metoden før sideinnholdet meldingen.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SignOutCleanupRequestMessage.Validate%2A>

trans-unit.source: The writer to which to write the message.
trans-unit.target: Skriveren som å skrive meldingen.

trans-unit.target: writeris .
